{"tid":2499312,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–運動為細胞帶來的其中一道影響","createTime":"2021-04-21T20:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T08:43:48.000Z","uid":38861,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"540e411f9baaf5f0b37c364802bb9631e3f672dc","tid":2499312,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T20:23:56.000Z","msg":"夏天，為大地帶來雨水。<br />\n林鄭，為香港帶來雞飯。<br />\n運動，又為我們的細胞帶來甚麼呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfX5ztfQSSdBZDWfT6UAWu67AxEWie48eaciUsVS64pMm?filename=tvYceQG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvYceQG.jpg&h=a537ea8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(圖2)細胞內的粒線體，是將營養轉化成為能源的地方。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmajFN69AYAtrtGevYcYs4UKmE2o7fiXk6jJJzJnxmQFhz?filename=aeUiUQJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaeUiUQJ.png&h=2725f869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖中紅色箭嘴所指的地方是粒線體內名為cristae的結構。<br />\n我們可以把cristae當作成為摺疊的枱布，這些枱布放置能夠將營養轉化成為能源的蛋白酶，提供細胞所需。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)從圖中可見，對比不做運動的人，勤做運動的人身體細胞的粒線體明顯地擁有更多摺疊的cristae結構(紅色箭嘴)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWBFGdSZ4KADnYmXPupQrZ9AFpNVAMceBLf31zQuiXsVm?filename=kKpnB35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKpnB35.png&h=d7b46c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這相信是細胞為了能夠製作更多的能源供運動所需，因此產生更多摺疊的cristae結構，從而放置更多能夠製造能源的蛋白酶。<br />\n<br />\n勤做運動，細胞便會隨之配合，改變粒線體的結構作持久提供能源之用。<br />\n<br />\n但亦有證據顯示，若然停做運動14日或以上，粒線體的結構便會逐漸開始打回原形。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=4dea621f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=09ee2366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5407961/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5407961%2F&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=80b136d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5407961/</a>"},{"pid":"34af26470d8f5107381e13bf566ff1407231fc74","tid":2499312,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T21:05:38.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"7ebd55f8f01bfffb1890ac964814d3f99d94c842","tid":2499312,"uid":54323,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:24:33.000Z","msg":"第二句就令我想打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a825d9406e6eb41b78831a6300b53a7dabec3b","tid":2499312,"uid":286385,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:25:44.000Z","msg":"若然停做運動14日或以上，粒線體的結構便會逐漸開始打回原形。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32